subject: Re: [junit] JUnit Question...
msgSnippet: David, This string does not appear in the JUnit source code.  It does appear to be a Windows error message.  What is the text of the call to assertEquals
messageBody:
David,

This string does not appear in the JUnit source code. It does appear to
be a Windows error message. What is the text of the call to
assertEquals giving you this error?

David Saff

Truong, David wrote:

> Does anyone recognize this message return by asserEquals() actual?

> Any feedback would be appreciate.
>
> Thanks,
> DT.
